schools.name: Southern School of Energy and Sustainability

data.description: Perfectly Priced & Close to Everything! This 2-story home features a bright open floor plan, fresh int. paint, Kitchen w/ SS appliances, new 2nd floor carpet, and spacious Loft which has great potential for an additional BR. Primary Suite offers a tray ceiling, huge soaking tub/shower combo, and WIC. Patio in the tree lined backyard-perfect for entertaining/unwinding after a long day. Walk to schools and enjoy close proximity to Chapel Hill, RDU/RTP, Brier Creek, tons of shopping, and incredible eateries. **Above ground pool conveys with home or it can be removed
